Class CastJiraConnectorBuilder

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    hudson.ExtensionPoint, hudson.model.Describable<hudson.tasks.Builder>, hudson.tasks.BuildStep

    public class CastJiraConnectorBuilder
extends hudson.tasks.Builder

    This plugin has been designed to transfer Cast Actions Plans to Jira

    When a build is performed, the perform(AbstractBuild, Launcher, BuildListener) method will be invoked.
